      <title>阿联酋总统华盛顿之行将把经济放在首位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/uae-looks-to-put-economics-first-on-president-s-trip-to-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国总统谢赫·穆罕默德·本·扎耶德将以该国统治者的身份首次访问华盛顿，届时他将优先讨论经济关系，而不是地缘政治问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/uae-looks-to-put-economics-first-on-president-s-trip-to-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 16:16:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《世界报》称马克龙将会见巴尼耶讨论法国内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/macron-to-meet-barnier-to-discuss-french-cabinet-le-monde-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《世界报》报道，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙将于周四晚上 7 点 15 分左右在巴黎会见法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶，讨论任命新内阁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/macron-to-meet-barnier-to-discuss-french-cabinet-le-monde-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:58:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行的举措为里夫斯带来了 40 亿英镑的救命钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/bank-of-england-moves-add-up-to-4-billion-lifeline-for-reeves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行向财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 提供了 40 亿英镑（53 亿美元）的救助金，以帮助缓解她所说的首份预算案的支出压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/bank-of-england-moves-add-up-to-4-billion-lifeline-for-reeves</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:58:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“大空头”投资者撤销对特朗普获胜的预测，称选举结果难料</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/eisman-rescinds-forecast-of-trump-win-calls-election-a-toss-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Neuberger Berman 高级投资组合经理史蒂夫·艾斯曼 (Steve Eisman) 表示，他“不知道”谁将赢得美国总统大选 — — 这推翻了早先对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 获胜的预测 — — 但他说，除了民主党大获全胜之外，在任何情况下市场都会表现良好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/eisman-rescinds-forecast-of-trump-win-calls-election-a-toss-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:55:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲对美联储大幅降息持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/europe-shows-wariness-to-jump-onto-fed-s-big-cut-bandwagon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从伦敦到法兰克福的政策制定者都表示，他们无意跟随美国迅速削减借贷成本，这在全球宽松速度问题上引发了跨大西洋联盟的新分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/europe-shows-wariness-to-jump-onto-fed-s-big-cut-bandwagon</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:43:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉脱维亚称北约应击落俄罗斯无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/nato-should-shoot-down-stray-russian-drones-latvia-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉脱维亚总统表示，北约需要有能力击落误入成员国领土的俄罗斯无人机，他呼吁加强北约东翼的防空力量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/nato-should-shoot-down-stray-russian-drones-latvia-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟 Illumina 败诉 荷兰呼吁获得更多交易权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/eu-s-illumina-defeat-sparks-dutch-call-for-more-deal-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧盟对更多小型交易进行审查的尝试遭到欧盟最高法院的否决后，荷兰竞争监管机构正在寻求加强权力，以调查这些可能破坏新兴科技市场竞争的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/eu-s-illumina-defeat-sparks-dutch-call-for-more-deal-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Steward Health 首席执行官因藐视法庭罪遭参议院委员会判刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/steward-health-ceo-held-in-criminal-contempt-by-senate-committee</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责调查 Steward Health Care 倒闭案的美国参议员周四投票通过了针对这家陷入困境的医疗系统的首席执行官的民事和刑事藐视法庭决议，因为他拒绝接受传票，拒绝就其在公司资金管理不善中所扮演的角色出庭作证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/steward-health-ceo-held-in-criminal-contempt-by-senate-committee</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:18:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加强战争讨论 爆炸设备死亡人数上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/exploding-gadgets-deathtoll-rises-in-lebanon-as-israel-steps-up-war-talk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地政府称，本周黎巴嫩发生的一系列对讲机和传呼机爆炸事件造成的死亡人数已上升至 37 人，这表明疑似以色列针对真主党武装分子的一系列袭击造成了多么严重的破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/exploding-gadgets-deathtoll-rises-in-lebanon-as-israel-steps-up-war-talk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 12:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国与欧盟同意在电动汽车关税表决前几天加强谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/china-eu-trade-officials-hold-last-ditch-talks-over-ev-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟和中国周四同意加强讨论，双方正寻求在仅剩几天的最后期限之前避免对电动汽车征收关税的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/china-eu-trade-officials-hold-last-ditch-talks-over-ev-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 10:58:21 GMT</pubDate>
